.TH LOA-REMOVE 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
remove \- Delete a book by reference
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> remove
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author).
.TP
Removes the book and also removes it from reading list entries.
.TP
Change is saved immediately.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> remove
